")),\n           go_to(label(\"test_b\")),\n         \"gcd_done\")) "},{"body":"\n    The first argument to\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"PYTHONINLINE","body":"make_machine"},{"body":"\n    is a list of register names. The next argument is a table (a list of\n    two-element lists) that pairs each operation name with a \n    Python function\n    that implements the operation (that is, produces the same output value\n    given the same input values). The last argument specifies the controller\n    as a list of labels and machine instructions, as in\n    section ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"REF","body":"5.1","href":"/sicpjs/5.1"},{"body":".\n  ","tag":"#text"}]},{"tag":"TEXT","id":"#p3","child":[{"body":"\n    To compute GCDs with this machine, we set the input registers, start the\n    machine, and examine the result when the simulation terminates:\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"SNIPPET","latex":false,"id":2,"eval":true,"prependLength":410,"program":"chap=4&prgrm=MQAgygkgwgCgniArAOgEwCh0BMCmAzEAcxwBcB9AJx0IEsBnEnCgCgFsBDAYwAsaA7HABoQVQmT7tWOAJQAudCEUjSAVwp8QHHvxzMARMXKj6jCnunNR4yTMy4CJOAAdd-BhRWcSNAPZ85CkpUJGoa3DjsWMxuJB5evv52+CAANj4+ANYqTmROFDSszHRwrABGPinCPi4U7N5+dAFKIABu7CkgALwg7HR0PpxFJeWVINVMdQmNgYrBoSDMTBQ+LMVlFcJ6KnwZfD4A7hrjtfUaALRnPX04ZSk45iA0BPRk2-Y6UW0p0jPNfzgpOg4EDhSLMEjsGgpZhfaRwpIENKZbJkFLsUoA5hojGA4TYgHWKRNJRfLpXfqDfEpQlCVLogHTZpzdQLJYrLH06kSKSbN74D50nEgC7km6lO4PJ6POivPjvASfdo-P4qkAM4EQqEwpU-bDJDgZHC5fKsGjeFpGnAADxy+EWNuEWl4AjxnMa8maUpenAaEL45GtTntTmJKs4ZJ9fAY7H9ZEDZC+Kl0geVquZGjRZSw7FkIE4vwBXplVLjNuDob+MToZKRWRyVI5OLorpxpfrnPLqZV6bpWZzjyjJDoBZSRco1BMTDb5Y9abJhnHtAYTDYXGdtOMy4obcXnd+TNULMzpWzuYXkcY---DJa22b8P3TmiO7fjHBHp19-3-Ei5pY4VjRmOgo1o8BoSk4SJayfQ3FnchhohcUamrVp+n5MZ5nVW13XTfd9hPbzEO47IauS7+SJRbVyWdvRqL5jlyuEI8kcgQTpRn3DhhNlKSJ-xwBgB3cCaA5FECxQlLyHCXkhmGzvxypl1JYv3vQg6Slu5TjnfF5tw--KD4rV-iI-epPyqua1Z-xrf-w76zVKLUMW3BbYzxILnR2bo3Yey9hWXAy9ujANVmAxB+8PqRzhqiTk050E10UFWfCyJ2w4kbBhfOO4Gz4M7mXCuycmaTxVFKI2-oOYNw9gQmGddjbsOvPrFeQ5O7NHVEwmG3dVbcT7p3Hsw9k7jwfA